Enum CigarOperator

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<CigarOperator>

    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<CigarOperator>

    public enum CigarOperator
extends java.lang.Enum<CigarOperator>
    The operators that can appear in a cigar string, and information about their disk representations.
